            "critical_success": "The creature is unaffected.",
            "success": "The creature takes half damage, and it takes a \u20135-foot circumstance penalty to its Speed for 1 minute, or until the creature or an ally spends three Interact actions to carefully remove the stakes.",
            "failure": "The triggering creature takes full damage. The creature takes a \u20135-foot circumstance penalty to its Speed, and any time it deals damage with a foot Strike (including as part of \nTrample\n or a similar ability), the creature takes 2d6 piercing damage. The effect lasts for 1 minute, or until the creature or an ally spends three Interact actions to carefully remove the stakes.",
